# chflags

##### make a samba shared folder writable, when doing an svn commit on OSX

   chflags  -R nouchg ./

##### Show/Hide files in Mac OS X

   chflags  nohidden ~/Library

##### make a samba shared folder writable, when doing an svn commit on OSX

   chflags  -R nouchg ./

##### Show/Hide files in Mac OS X

   chflags  nohidden ~/Library
